Privacy Policy & Customer Support
Privacy Policy
We, The Chroma Network, do not use third-party ads or whatnot in the app Chroma and collect no user data or cookies. Your settings and data are stored securely and safely on your own device; we don't have access to that. Any future updates that may affect data usage will be communicated transparently.
Support
Find yourself in need of Customer Support? Feel free to write a review in the App Store and our staff will make sure to get back to you as fast as possible!